Content-Type: application/json

### Валидация карты - успешная
POST http://localhost:3005/payment/validate-card
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cardNumber": "4111111111111111",
  "cvc": "123",
  "expiry": "12/25",
  "cardHolder": "IVAN IVANOV"
}

### Валидация карты - ошибка
POST http://localhost:3005/payment/validate-card
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cardNumber": "123",
  "cvc": "12",
  "expiry": "13/20",
  "cardHolder": ""
}

